{"tid":1740445,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒：普捷天奴上週被要求主動請辭；紀錄片拍攝成導火線","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T10:30:26.000Z","uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff6e60af74c6c767a38a96641762408f9aa536f","tid":1740445,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/sportsyeah.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/4705C978-A70E-4DE7-8A92-CE1BB28379E1.jpeg?resize=1600%2C900&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F4705C978-A70E-4DE7-8A92-CE1BB28379E1.jpeg%3Fresize%3D1600%252C900%26ssl%3D1&h=96b6b600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱刺宣布和領隊普捷天奴（Mauricio Pochettino）解約。各大英國媒體報導，熱刺主席利維（Daniel Levy）上週已要求普帥主動辭職被拒。而且，這位阿根廷教頭離隊，原來跟球隊拍攝Amazon紀錄片的計劃有關。<br />\n<br />\n《Telegraph》記者Sam Wallace和Matt Law的報道指，利維認為解僱普帥的決定是無可奈何的選擇，畢竟上季季尾和今季季初球隊在聯賽的成績難以服眾。由於熱刺內部的種種問題，下一輪對韋斯咸的比賽不容有失，利維決定要跟普帥分手。教練團成員：Jesus Perez、Miguel D&rsquo;Agostino 及 Antoni Jimenez將跟隨普帥離隊，整佃團隊獲得1250萬鎊解約金賠償。<br />\n<br />\n另一個令普帥離開的導火絈口，是球隊拍攝紀錄片。在10月，熱刺曾宣佈，Amazon 在今季為球隊拍攝名為《All or Nothing》的紀錄片，預計於明年上映。該紀錄片將會記錄熱刺場內場外的動態，包括更衣室和訓練場內主帥之間的互動。對上支接受拍攝計劃的球隊，是上季聯賽冠軍曼城。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》指，這部紀錄片將為熱刺帶來大約800萬鎊的收入，但普捷天奴認為球隊並沒有做好接受外來人拍攝的準備。普捷天奴表示：「這給我們帶來很多壓力。我覺得我不再僅僅是一名教練，而更像是紀錄片製片人兼主帥。」"},{"pid":"ad9860617fb6fe549588b456ee8dd34f02e67819","tid":1740445,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"普狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1afc71ea9d938d8913def0a562437e324f141a7","tid":1740445,"uid":103230,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"熱狗真係柒到出煙<br />\n乜盃都冇學人鏝拍紀錄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f92843ffc5132a8d31cb1ca84a0b81da53f5e01","tid":1740445,"uid":40940,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b1afc71ea9d938d8913def0a562437e324f141a7","tid":1740445,"uid":103230,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"熱狗真係柒到出煙<br />\n乜盃都冇學人鏝拍紀錄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"係個班主柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fe913e495fc8620e5ea5cbe575ab359d07b579","tid":1740445,"uid":240245,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"個紀錄片個名仲要叫《All or Nothing》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458f181f49fc33413f0dc3e6bce53c29d8f86090","tid":1740445,"uid":85924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"咁咪好，變左nothing"},{"pid":"c3811ed7d391f699b40b4dff9ba54349c4216489","tid":1740445,"uid":70362,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"f1fe913e495fc8620e5ea5cbe575ab359d07b579","tid":1740445,"uid":240245,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"個紀錄片個名仲要叫《All or Nothing》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:50:51.000Z","msg":"nothing搵熱狗拍match曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd71f7871be1130ed196b41